"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-26-Live-Opening-day-for-2024-Olympic-Games-in-France-1vyeVWgmMVy-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  The\\u00a0opening ceremony\\u00a0for the\\u00a0Paris 2024\\u00a0is set to begin at 7:30 p.m. on Friday. Instead of a traditional march into a stadium, about 6,800 athletes will parade on more than 90 boats on the Seine River for six kilometers (3.7 miles). Before the ceremony, join us and check out the various scenes in Paris, from a skyline shot to people arriving at the venue to see how the host city is prepared.  CGTN  Copied  The\\u00a0opening ceremony\\u00a0for the\\u00a0Paris 2024\\u00a0is set to begin at 7:30 p.m. on Friday. Instead of a traditional march into a stadium, about 6,800 athletes will parade on more than 90 boats on the Seine River for six kilometers (3.7 miles). Before the ceremony, join us and check out the various scenes in Paris, from a skyline shot to people arriving at the venue to see how the host city is prepared.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"